OL,7,FA solicitor says there "will be more
OL,8,Fdeaths" at a mental health trust
OL,9,Fprosecuted for failing a teenager and
OL,10,Fmother who took their own lives while
OL,11,Funder its care.
OL,13,FAlistair Smith represented the
OL,14,Ffamilies of patients who died while
OL,15,Fbeing cared for by the Tees, Esk and
OL,16,FWear Valleys NHS Foundation Trust.
