OL,7,FHis warning follows the sentencing of
OL,8,Fthe trust on Friday which saw it
OL,9,Fordered to pay a fine of #200,000
OL,10,Fafter pleading guilty to failing to
OL,11,Fprovide safe care and treatment to
OL,12,FChristie Harnett, 17, and Patient X.
OL,14,FChristie, from Newton Aycliffe, took
OL,15,Fher life in June 2019 while being
OL,16,Fcared for at West Lane Hospital, in
OL,17,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,19,FPatient X took her life while on an
OL,20,Fadult ward at Roseberry Park Hospital,
OL,21,Fin the same city, in late 2020.
