OL,8,FTyne Tees what happened.
OL,10,FWhat happened to Christie Harnett?
OL,12,FWhen Christie Harnett was admitted to
OL,13,FWest Lane Hospital in 2017 with an
OL,14,Feating disorder, her mother hoped she
OL,15,Fwould get better.
OL,17,FBut that did not happen and two years
OL,18,Flater she took her own life there.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/23
