OL,7,FCharlotte Harnett, Christie's mother
OL,8,Fsaid: "I didn't want her to be in
OL,9,Fhospital. As my child, I wanted to
OL,10,Flook after her. I wanted to make it
OL,11,Fbetter.
OL,13,F"As the weeks went on and she was
OL,14,Fgetting worse and worse and worse, I
OL,15,Fdidn't know what to do. I didn't know
OL,16,Fwho to turn to.
OL,18,F"I was asking staff members why she'd
OL,19,Fbeen allowed to self-harm."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/23
