OL,7,FIn March 2019, Christie tried to take
OL,8,Fher own life using taps in her
OL,9,Fbathroom at the hospital and was put
OL,10,Fon life support.
OL,12,FJust days earlier she told her family
OL,13,Fshe felt unsafe.
OL,15,F"She actually sent a message saying,
OL,16,F'I'm going to end up dead, if I'm
OL,17,Fhonest'," continued Charlotte.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/23
