OL,7,F"I had a lot of missed calls on my
OL,8,Fphone, I knew it was something
OL,9,Fserious," she told ITV News Tyne Tees.
OL,10,F"I rang Charlotte, and she said,
OL,11,FChristie's in intensive care on life
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,F"I couldn't understand how it got to
OL,15,Fthat point, how her being in hospital
OL,16,Fbeing monitored has allowed that to
OL,17,Fhappen. It didn't make sense."
OL,19,FChristie did recover and went back to
OL,20,FWest Lane. But her family said things
OL,21,Fwere only getting worse.
