OL,7,FBack at the hospital, Charlotte
OL,8,Fdescribed witnessing "girls walking
OL,9,Faround, blood dripping down their
OL,10,Ffaces, marks on their arms, which had
OL,11,Fbeen cutting".
OL,13,FShe feared the worst would happen to
OL,14,Fher teenage daughter - a child who was
OL,15,F"funny", who "loved singing dancing,
OL,16,Fclothes, make up" and who was "like
OL,17,Fsunshine" in her family's lives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/23
