OL,7,F"I told the staff," Charlotte
OL,8,Fexplained. "I said something needs to
OL,9,Fbe done because someone's going to end
OL,10,Fup dead. And they didn't listen."
OL,12,FIn June 2019, Christie made another
OL,13,Fattempt on her life in a bathroom at
OL,14,FWest Lane. She died four days later on
OL,15,F27 June.
OL,17,FLike in March, Christie had hurt
OL,18,Fherself using taps in the bathroom -
OL,19,Ftaps the trust had been warned were a
OL,20,Frisk in January of that year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/23
