OL,7,F"I remember Charlotte saying to me
OL,8,Fthat she wasn't coming back this
OL,9,Ftime," said Casey. "And I was saying
OL,10,Fto Charlotte, 'don't say it, don't say
OL,11,Fit'.
OL,13,F"She's not here because she was failed
OL,14,Fand it hits you in random moments. You
OL,15,Fcan be out and smell a perfume and it
OL,16,Fwill trigger me.
OL,18,F"The smell, a sound, a song. And she's
OL,19,Fnot here."
