OL,7,FCharlotte continued: "I didn't ever
OL,8,Fthink that I would lose a child, and I
OL,9,Fhave. And it's horrible."
OL,11,FWhat happened to Patient X
OL,13,FIn August 2019 West Lane Hospital was
OL,14,Fshut down following the death of
OL,15,Fanother patient - Nadia Sharif, from
OL,16,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,18,FThree months later the trust's chief
OL,19,Fexecutive Colin Martin announced his
OL,20,Fretirement.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/23
