OL,7,FBy June 2020 the trust had a new boss,
OL,8,FBrent Kilmurray, who had previously
OL,9,Fworked at the trust in a senior role .
OL,11,FIt was under his leadership that a
OL,12,Fsecond patient, Patient X died, and
OL,13,Fwhose death the trust is also been
OL,14,Fprosecuted over.
OL,16,FShe has been referred to as Patient X
OL,17,Fto protect her identity in order to
OL,18,Fsafeguard her children.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/23
