OL,7,FPatient X's mother told ITV News Tyne
OL,8,FTees: "She wanted to get better - she
OL,9,Fwanted to come home to her children.
OL,10,FShe was a good mum. She was my baby."
OL,11,FPatient X died on an adult ward at
OL,12,FRoseberry Park Hospital in
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough in late 2020.
OL,15,FLike Christie, she took her own life
OL,16,Fusing taps in a bathroom.
OL,18,F"I think they should be ashamed of
OL,19,Fthemselves. I think what they've put
OL,20,Fthese families through is absolutely
OL,21,Fridiculous.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/23
