OL,7,F"When this court case is over, they
OL,8,Fwalk away and forget all about it. We
OL,9,Fare left with the aftermath of the
OL,10,Fdecisions that weren't made properly."
OL,12,FTimeline of events
OL,14,FUrgent calls for change
OL,16,FAlistair Smith has been representing
OL,17,Fmany families who lost loved ones
OL,18,Funder the care of Tees, Esk and Wear
OL,19,FValleys NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,20,Fincluding Christie Harnett and Patient
OL,21,FX.
