OL,7,FHe told ITV News Tyne Tees: "The care
OL,8,Fmust have been absolutely appalling,
OL,9,Fbecause it's not easy to bring a
OL,10,Fprosecution of a trust and it isn't
OL,11,Fdone often.
OL,13,F"And so the substandard care must be
OL,14,Fso low to reach the criminal standard."
OL,16,FIn the case of Christie Harnett he
OL,17,Fbelieves the police should
OL,18,Freinvestigate what happened at West
OL,19,FLane Hospital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/23
