OL,7,FAlmost five years on from Christie's
OL,8,Fdeath, there are concerns things are
OL,9,Fnot getting better.
OL,11,FThe latest inspection by the Care
OL,12,FQuality Commission shows it is a trust
OL,13,Fthat still 'requires improvement'.
OL,15,FFollowing the sentencing of the trust
OL,16,Fover the deaths of Christie and
OL,17,FPatient X, there are renewed calls for
OL,18,Fits chief executive to step down.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G17/23
