OL,7,FIn a message to Brent Kilmurray, Mr
OL,8,FSmith urged: "Please resign. Please do
OL,9,Fthe honourable thing.
OL,11,F"If you do that it gives the trust a
OL,12,Fbetter chance of improving which is
OL,13,Fwhat all the people, all the patients
OL,14,Fwant for this trust."
OL,16,FAsked if Mr Smith thought patients at
OL,17,Fthe trust are now safe, he answered
OL,18,F"no".
OL,20,FAsked if Mr Smith thought there would
OL,21,Fbe more deaths, he answered "yes".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G18/23
