OL,7,FCharlotte, Christie's mother, said her
OL,8,Fdeath had "destroyed" the lives of the
OL,9,Ffamily - including her five other
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FShe and Christie's grandmother Casey
OL,13,Fsay "someone needs to be held
OL,14,Faccountable".
OL,16,F"If failings took a life anywhere
OL,17,Felse, people would be held to
OL,18,Faccount," added Casey.
OL,20,FTheir feelings are echoed by Mr Smith
OL,21,Fand the mother of Patent X.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G19/23
