OL,7,FMr Smith said: "There's a lot of
OL,8,Fpeople in senior management jobs who
OL,9,Ffailed, nothing's happened to them and
OL,10,Fthere's been no personal
OL,11,Faccountability for that."
OL,13,FWhile Patient X's mother added:
OL,14,F"They're not just numbers, They're not
OL,15,Fjust nameless faces. They are family
OL,16,Fmembers, they are mothers, they are
OL,17,Fdaughters. Please just remember that."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G20/23
