OL,7,FFor many years, Christie's mother said
OL,8,Fshe carried the guilt of her
OL,9,Fdaughter's death. But now she knows
OL,10,Fshe was not to blame:
OL,12,F"No matter what I did it wouldn't have
OL,13,Fchanged anything," she said. "It
OL,14,Fwasn't my fault. It was their fault."
OL,16,FThe Trust's CEO, Brent Kilmurray, has
OL,17,Falso given a own statement, which
OL,18,Freads: "As we made clear in court
OL,19,Ftoday, we're deeply sorry for the
OL,20,Fevents that led to these tragedies.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G21/23
