OL,7,F"We didn't provide the care these two
OL,8,Fpeople deserved, and the guilty pleas
OL,9,Freflect that. Of course, that's no
OL,10,Fconsolation for Patient X and
OL,11,FChristy's loved ones, for which I
OL,12,Foffer our heartfelt apologies.
OL,14,F"The CQC has acknowledged in our
OL,15,Flatest inspection that improvements
OL,16,Fhave been made since then, however
OL,17,Ftoday is about being accountable and
OL,18,Four thoughts are with the families at
OL,19,Fthis incredibly difficult time."
